<br>
1) the hole    Pet actually follows me in there instead of wandering all over the freaking place like they do in kunark dungeons.<br>
<br>
2) Skyshrine    Pretty straightforward place with good pathing so far.<br>
<br>
Worst pathing <br>
<br>
1)Hateplane.  Wanna see a nightmare?  Summon a pet on the wall and watch it take off.<br>
